225
00:53:05,044 --> 00:53:07,840
Motherfucker,
what do you mean "cremate him"?

226
00:53:09,133 --> 00:53:12,553
You should have told me. I wouldn't
have dolled him up, fucker.

227
00:53:12,553 --> 00:53:14,555
God, rest in peace.

228
00:53:14,555 --> 00:53:16,725
