will leave you this letter.

267
01:06:01,470 --> 01:06:05,266
By the time you read it...

268
01:06:05,266 --> 01:06:08,437
I would have been gone to settle
some kind of date,

269
01:06:08,437 --> 01:06:11,273
an unfinished business.

